column2: select top # p.fieldId, p.objId into mydb.galaxy_sort1# from Galaxy as p where p.dec > = # AND p.dec < # AND p.mode = # AND (p.flags & CAST (# AS BIGINT) ) = # AND (p.flags & CAST (# AS BIGINT) ) = CAST (# AS BIGINT) AND exists (select g.fieldId, count (g.objId) from Galaxy as g where p.fieldId = g.fieldId group by fieldId having count (g.objId) > #) order by p.fieldId asc
